sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Gateway
    participant AuthService

    Note over User, Frontend: Scenario A: Unauthenticated user tries /admin
    User->>Frontend: Navigate to /admin
    Frontend->>Frontend: Protected sees no session.token
    Frontend-->>User: Redirect to /login

    Note over User, Frontend: Scenario B: Applicant user tries /admin
    User->>Frontend: Navigate to /admin
    Frontend->>Frontend: Protected checks role and denies access
    Frontend-->>User: Redirect to /dashboard

    Note over User, Frontend: Scenario C: Invalid/expired JWT on protected API call
    Frontend->>Gateway: GET /gateway/admin/applications with Bearer token
    Gateway->>Gateway: JWT auth fails
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 401 Unauthorized
    Frontend-->>User: Show error or redirect to login
